{"type":null,"faqId":49743,"title":"华为智能手表_如何开始单次运动、查看单次运动数据？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body5792039\"><ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__ol4566175918304\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__li34047137154045\">在手表主界面向左滑动一下，选择 <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b064e_phtq1.png\" width=\"26.63325\" height=\"26.63325\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span> <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__b20388238162250\">锻炼</strong>，点击 <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b064f_v9uxx.png\" width=\"29.226750000000003\" height=\"28.82775\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span> ，设置单次锻炼的<strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__b37426388151758\"> 时间 / 卡路里 </strong>。<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__p76964018355\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0650_pysp0.png\" width=\"399\" height=\"123.78974847793592\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__p11424440143943\">或者在手表亮屏时，对着主屏幕说“你好，安卓”唤起倾听界面后，说一声“打开锻炼”开始单次运动。</p></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__li44969860154045\">上下滑动屏幕设置目标，点击 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__b31023754154319\">开始</strong>。<ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__ul42127289135915\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__li43601282135915\">点击 <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0651_wtgkb.png\" width=\"29.226750000000003\" height=\"29.027250000000002\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span> 暂停记录。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__li42042959135915\">点击 <span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0652_atudp.png\" width=\"29.226750000000003\" height=\"29.027250000000002\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span> 停止运动并查看运动数据。</li></ul><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__p63138571165449\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/b0653_1kbd5.png\" width=\"465.53325\" height=\"144.53775000000002\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329152__p10297903114716\">感谢您支持并使用华为手表，关于手表运动计步的更多操作，请您在Wi-Fi环境下参阅视频教程：<a href=\"http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQyODIzOTEwMA==.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://v.youku.com/v_show/id_XMTQyODIzOTEwMA==.html</a></p></li></ol></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":211,"faqType":"运动及健康监测","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329152","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Sports-Health-Monitoring","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448590133000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10,Mercury-G101,Mercury-G201","visitedTimes":53,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"单次，运动","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}